# 脵聛脴搂脹聦脵聞 脴陋脵聠脴赂脹聦脵聟脴搂脴陋 脵聟脴颅脹聦脴路脹聦 - galaxy-vast
# =====================================================================
# 脴搂脹聦脵聠 脵聛脴搂脹聦脵聞 脴卤脴搂 脷漏脵戮脹聦 脷漏脵聠脹聦脴炉 脴篓脵聡 .env 脵聢 脵聟脵聜脴搂脴炉脹聦脴卤 脴卤脴搂 脵戮脴卤 脷漏脵聠脹聦脴炉
# 脵聡脴卤脷炉脴虏 脵聛脴搂脹聦脵聞 .env 脴卤脴搂 脴炉脴卤 脷炉脹聦脴陋 脷漏脴搂脵聟脹聦脴陋 脵聠脷漏脵聠脹聦脴炉!
# =====================================================================

# ----- 脴陋脵聠脴赂脹聦脵聟脴搂脴陋 脴陋脵聞脷炉脴卤脴搂脵聟 -----
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=your_telegram_bot_token_here
TELEGRAM_ADMIN_CHAT_IDS=123456789,987654321

# ----- 脴陋脵聠脴赂脹聦脵聟脴搂脴陋 脴炉脹聦脴陋脴搂脴篓脹聦脴鲁 Supabase -----
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_anon_key_here
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your_service_role_key_here

# ----- 脴陋脵聠脴赂脹聦脵聟脴搂脴陋 API -----
API_HOST=0.0.0.0
API_PORT=8000
# 鬲賵賱蹖丿 亘丕: python -c "import secrets; print(secrets.token_urlsafe(32))"
API_SECRET_KEY=REPLACE_WITH_GENERATED_SECRET
API_DEBUG=false

# ----- 脴陋脵聠脴赂脹聦脵聟脴搂脴陋 脵聞脴搂脹聦脴鲁脵聠脴鲁 -----
LICENSE_SECRET_KEY=your_license_secret_key
LICENSE_SERVER_URL=https://your-license-server.com
LICENSE_CHECK_INTERVAL_HOURS=6

# ----- 脴陋脵聠脴赂脹聦脵聟脴搂脴陋 脵聟脴鹿脴搂脵聟脵聞脵聡 -----
DEFAULT_RISK_PERCENT=1.0
MAX_DAILY_LOSS_PERCENT=5.0
MAX_SIMULTANEOUS_TRADES=3
MIN_RISK_REWARD_RATIO=1.5
MINIMUM_ENTRY_SCORE=65.0

# ----- 脴陋脵聠脴赂脹聦脵聟脴搂脴陋 脴陋脴颅脵聞脹聦脵聞 -----
DEFAULT_TIMEFRAME=H1
ENABLE_MULTI_TIMEFRAME=true
ENABLE_SMC_ENGINE=true
ENABLE_PRICE_ACTION=true
ENABLE_DECISION_ENGINE=true

# ----- 脴陋脵聠脴赂脹聦脵聟脴搂脴陋 脵聞脴搂脷炉 -----
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
LOG_FILE_PATH=logs/galaxy-vast.log
LOG_MAX_SIZE_MB=50
LOG_BACKUP_COUNT=5

# ----- 脴陋脵聠脴赂脹聦脵聟脴搂脴陋 脴搂脵聟脵聠脹聦脴陋 -----
# 鬲賵賱蹖丿 亘丕: python -c "import secrets; print(secrets.token_hex(32))"
JWT_SECRET_KEY=REPLACE_WITH_GENERATED_SECRET_MIN_32_CHARS
JWT_ALGORITHM=HS256
JWT_EXPIRE_MINUTES=1440

# ----- 脴陋脵聠脴赂脹聦脵聟脴搂脴陋 CORS -----
CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:5173

# ----- 脴陋脵聠脴赂脹聦脵聟脴搂脴陋 Redis (脴搂脴庐脴陋脹聦脴搂脴卤脹聦) -----
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379/0
REDIS_CACHE_TTL=300

# ----- 脴陋脵聠脴赂脹聦脵聟脴搂脴陋 脴鲁脴麓脵聠 -----
LONDON_SESSION_OPEN=08:00
LONDON_SESSION_CLOSE=17:00
NEW_YORK_SESSION_OPEN=13:00
NEW_YORK_SESSION_CLOSE=22:00
TOKYO_SESSION_OPEN=00:00
TOKYO_SESSION_CLOSE=09:00
SYDNEY_SESSION_OPEN=22:00
SYDNEY_SESSION_CLOSE=07:00

# ----- 讴賱蹖丿賴丕蹖 丕賲賳蹖鬲蹖 license -----
LICENSE_ENCRYPTION_KEY=REPLACE_WITH_32_BYTE_KEY
LICENSE_SIGNATURE_KEY=REPLACE_WITH_SIGNATURE_KEY
